{
  "stem": "10587.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and they took most everything away from you, whatever you had, except they'd leave you with a suitcase.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were limited, too, because you also carrying this stuff.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You were not-- so I remember that it was a cramped quarters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was very-- everything was limited.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You couldn't take a bath.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You couldn't-- you had to wait in line if you want to go to the bathroom, because there was a lot of people bunched together.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were working in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My-- my father used to go to work every morning, and I was going to-- I was working in the factory, I think.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For uniforms.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I was sewing buttons on the uniform.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "German uniforms.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] then it didn't take that long, must have been already in-- it was in '43, when they started to liquidate the-- the ghetto, and they would transport Monday.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I came home, and it was the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a horrible time because while we were away, [SIGHS] they took my mother into Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[CRYING] And this-- I never saw her-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I never saw her again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were left, my-- my father and my younger brother, Joshua.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know how they did not take him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe he was hiding somewhere or playing with someone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- but they were starting to liquidate, so where we lived, there was like a place where they had an apartment complex, where there was a basement, so-- We're gonna have to stop here and change the reel.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
